casebody.data:
No. 167,

Misc.

Coffey v. Fay, Warden. Alfred I. Rosner and Martin B. Rosner for petitioner.

C. A. 2d Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas and Mr. Justice Fortas are of the opinion that certiorari should he granted. The Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
